Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.92,0:02:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fs42\fad(300,300)}{\move(720,60,720,8)}{\blur3}字幕重校、压制：巴洛克哥特
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.47,0:00:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.95,0:00:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.00,0:00:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是罗伊·穆斯唐中佐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.04,0:00:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}鄙人爱德华·艾尔利克
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.63,0:00:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}鄙人? 你不用那么紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.34,0:00:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是 我们马上就要坐九点二十分出发开往中央的火车
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.02,0:00:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}知道了 不 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.31,0:00:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}前面不是还有一趟么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.97,0:00:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}倒是有 不过那一趟好像已经要出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.03,0:00:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就坐那趟车
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.58,0:00:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.36,0:00:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}叫你坐就坐!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.92,0:00:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿尔 这边来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.04,0:00:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快点!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.20,0:00:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fn方正隶变_GBK\b1\pos(720,900)\fs60\c&H00DEE0DD}穆斯唐中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.36,0:00:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}试试他的运气
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.75,0:01:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人没有什么牺牲的话就什么都得不到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.19,0:01:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为了得到什么东西 就需要付出同等的代价
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.68,0:01:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就是炼金术的等价交换原则
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.41,0:01:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那时我们坚信那就是世界的真实
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.71,0:03:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fn华康雅艺体W6\pos(720,760)\3c&HD3CF9C&\fs70}快跑! 机械铠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.47,0:03:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真不知道穆斯唐中佐在打什么主意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.85,0:03:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他是什么样的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.04,0:03:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥 我很可怕么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.21,0:03:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没有 没这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.26,0:03:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂喂 那儿有个怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.67,0:03:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怪?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.04,0:03:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}玛琳 不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.09,0:03:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}安静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.20,0:03:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是好有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.84,0:03:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在火车里还穿着铠甲 真是很喜欢铠甲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.69,0:04:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是啦 我们并不是什么可疑人物…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.36,0:04:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你看你看 人家喜欢你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.80,0:04:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.98,0:04:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很帅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.71,0:04:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好了 玛琳 安分点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.20,0:04:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fn方正隶变_GBK\b1\pos(720,890)\fs60\c&H00DEE0DD}哈克罗将军
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.84,0:04:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}玩得太疯 累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.61,0:04:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}旅行能这样一路顺风真是太好了 哈克罗将军
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.04,0:04:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}听说东部的形势不太稳定 也不过如此嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.03,0:05:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fn方正隶变_GBK\b1\pos(1050,845)\fs60\c&H00DEE0DD}法尔曼准尉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.82,0:05:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是的 上头的人还真是悠闲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.77,0:05:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}说起来休斯少佐现在在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.42,0:05:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是 为了那件事去跟穆斯唐中佐联络了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.98,0:05:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那件事?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.73,0:05:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}算了 那样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.06,0:05:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我说啊 老婆她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.70,0:05:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fn方正隶变_GBK\b1\pos(720,890)\fs60\c&H00DEE0DD}休斯少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.36,0:05:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知是不是因为怀孕了 变得越来越漂亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.58,0:05:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么说好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.09,0:05:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就像下凡到人间的天使…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.04,0:05:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}又断线了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.47,0:05:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}通讯状况真差
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.33,0:05:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.18,0:05:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}让人受不了的是你才对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.50,0:05:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样的话不再去巡视一遍真让人放心不下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.20,0:05:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂喂?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.08,0:05:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.45,0:05:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对了对了 要是小孩明天就出生的话怎么办好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.43,0:05:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}休斯 那些话我都听了有五十遍了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.27,0:05:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要问这种事别给我打电话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.77,0:06:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}直接找你老婆去!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.38,0:06:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我打了啊 刚才就已经打了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.71,0:06:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就不要问我!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.80,0:06:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fn方正隶变_GBK\b1\pos(720,890)\fs60\c&H00DEE0DD}霍克埃少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.07,0:06:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不好意思 打断一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.57,0:06:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少佐 给你一个忠告
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.57,0:06:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}才怀孕五个月不可能生出来的!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.49,0:06:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么 这电话听得不大清啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.07,0:06:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好…好可疑…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.85,0:06:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好了 休斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.45,0:06:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}刚刚确认了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.93,0:06:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没有无线电干扰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.66,0:06:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那么怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.22,0:06:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}发现什么可疑的人了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.97,0:06:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.89,0:06:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}虽然这么说 但是乘客的数量比预想的多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.33,0:06:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也说不定在单间里…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.74,0:06:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.79,0:06:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}找到了!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.74,0:06:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}找到了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.06,0:06:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}找到了 非常可疑的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.19,0:07:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.28,0:07:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}穿着那—么大的铠甲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.66,0:07:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}铠甲?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.74,0:07:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个人没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.11,0:07:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}跟他在一起的应该还有个豆丁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.82,0:07:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}豆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.61,0:07:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}…丁?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.89,0:07:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没错啊 果然有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.84,0:07:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的好矮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.14,0:07:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谁是小得让人看不见的豆丁!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.82,0:07:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是的 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.46,0:07:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我可没有那样说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.26,0:07:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}安静 都把双手举起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.97,0:08:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们这些混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.19,0:08:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你好啊 哈克罗将军
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.24,0:08:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}休斯 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.47,0:08:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}出什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.76,0:08:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}休斯!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.20,0:08:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}联络巴尔特
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.29,0:08:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}无线电已经被占领了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.01,0:08:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好像没有人用过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.33,0:08:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}果然那帮家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.41,0:08:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哈克罗将军从来中央的列车上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.53,0:08:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}给中央司令部的紧急联络
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.63,0:08:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}接通
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.69,0:08:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是我…中佐? 是穆斯唐中佐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.71,0:09:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是东部解放战线青之团的巴尔特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.34,0:09:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这班列车已经被我们占领了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.88,0:09:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要求是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.18,0:09:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别装傻了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.86,0:09:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们与一个同伴忽然失去联系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.09,0:09:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是递交声明给你们的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.94,0:09:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.72,0:09:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.59,0:09:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把关在第八监狱里 我们的首领带到中央车站来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.11,0:09:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}交换人质
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.68,0:09:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好吧 但是你不要杀任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.79,0:09:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不然的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.81,0:09:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样好吗 声明在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.59,0:09:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是让将军死了 我们要负责任的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.28,0:09:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没关系 把事件解决不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.68,0:09:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我已经做了充分的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.55,0:09:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}穆斯唐那个男人 到底在打什么主意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.73,0:10:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是敢轻举妄动的话 不光是你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.20,0:10:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}全车的乘客都要没命 给我想清楚!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.98,0:10:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.87,0:10:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.18,0:10:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你这混蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.42,0:10:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们这么干想怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.78,0:11:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是惹来更多他们的同伙的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.41,0:11:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没错 要是不抵抗 我们起码能安全到达中央啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.32,0:11:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没错 是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.99,0:11:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.14,0:11:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你问我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.85,0:11:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.63,0:11:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.68,0:11:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对不起啊 哥哥们会想办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.20,0:11:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}走吧 阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.74,0:11:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们两个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.99,0:12:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真丢脸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.22,0:12:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.68,0:12:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只是炼金术师罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.06,0:12:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是吗 我叫法尔曼 是准尉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.64,0:12:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}军人? 完全看不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.00,0:12:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}穿成这样是有原因的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.46,0:12:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其实在首节车厢里…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.56,0:12:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那么犯人的目的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.89,0:12:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}让这么多人受牵连
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.48,0:12:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿尔 我从上面过去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.48,0:12:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}下面的就交给你和这个人了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.25,0:12:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.75,0:12:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不行了 快来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.48,0:12:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}从后面来的 情况不大妥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.82,0:13:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还是不要开枪比较…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.81,0:13:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好疼啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.76,0:13:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}本来想跟你说 开枪的话流弹很危险的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.89,0:13:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.88,0:13:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还是不要开枪比较…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.75,0:13:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}巴尔特
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.01,0:13:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}后面的车厢联络不上了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.30,0:13:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.85,0:13:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}果然是有什么阴谋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.83,0:13:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们还是放弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.67,0:13:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}投降 然后把乘客都放了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.29,0:13:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们是不可能得逞的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.82,0:13:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能发号施令的只有我 将军
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.36,0:13:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再把整列车检查一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.77,0:13:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}车厢的外面也要一点不漏地搜查
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.66,0:14:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.17,0:14:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能上到这挺不容易啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.06,0:14:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我叫休斯 你是爱德华·艾尔利克吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.23,0:14:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.81,0:14:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我从穆斯唐中佐那儿听说过你的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.35,0:14:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}从中佐那儿?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.96,0:14:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.92,0:14:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那么 就请协助我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.06,0:14:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我已经都调查好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.14,0:14:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.12,0:14:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是什么人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.41,0:15:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有了有了 接招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.91,0:15:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.17,0:15:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.14,0:15:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.92,0:15:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要乱搞有如火车生命的煤水车啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.93,0:15:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.64,0:15:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}煤水车?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.08,0:15:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不行啊 巴尔特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.95,0:15:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}上面有个不得了的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.86,0:15:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}巴尔特 其他的车厢也都失去联系了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.84,0:16:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}说是有个穿着巨大铠甲的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.26,0:16:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别吵!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.37,0:16:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}犯罪集团的诸位 能听得见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.58,0:16:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.68,0:16:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}听好 你们这帮家伙竟敢威胁乘客
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.80,0:16:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}赶快释放人质
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.28,0:16:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你就是穆斯唐派来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.99,0:16:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你要是再捣乱的话 我就把人质一个一个地…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.75,0:16:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你还真有气势呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.61,0:16:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.27,0:16:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是…水…管?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.71,0:16:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}注意 诸位人质 请躲好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.08,0:16:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.24,0:17:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.87,0:17:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好了 不要动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.42,0:17:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你就是主谋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.84,0:17:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么了 滚出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.62,0:17:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.17,0:17:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}干掉将军之前 先从你开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.37,0:17:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.98,0:17:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原来都是用机械铠的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.26,0:17:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样的小鬼居然…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.39,0:17:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}军队居然连孩子都利用的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.02,0:17:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小鬼小鬼的 难听死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.02,0:17:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过 我可不是被利用的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.23,0:17:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小子 我告诉你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.86,0:17:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我以前也是军人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.82,0:18:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个时候 我想要更完美的武装
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.31,0:18:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是军队好像不喜欢我这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.01,0:18:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们是害怕我一个人变强
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.37,0:18:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我做了这个手术以后
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.54,0:18:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}随随便便地就被军队遗弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.82,0:18:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以…所以 我要把军队打垮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.26,0:18:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你也明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.53,0:18:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}既然你有那样的手臂 那也应该是你的目的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.55,0:18:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想要变得比任何人都强
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.32,0:18:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.71,0:18:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要把我这条胳膊和你的那玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.02,0:18:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}混为一谈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.66,0:19:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是厉害的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.52,0:19:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"不要杀任何人"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.77,0:19:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}虽然我这么说了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.74,0:19:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我没想到你这么听话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.31,0:19:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你就是穆斯唐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.10,0:20:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}厉…厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.58,0:20:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我手下留情了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.76,0:20:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}身体受的伤不像看上去那样严重
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.17,0:20:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我叫罗伊·穆斯唐 军衔是中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.17,0:20:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}同时 也叫做"焰之炼金术师"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.69,0:20:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你可记好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.58,0:20:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那家伙就是穆斯唐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.55,0:20:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.82,0:20:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}中佐 一开始你就全知道了 所以才让我们坐那趟车的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.92,0:20:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也不是全知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.12,0:20:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不说这个 我有个好消息
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.92,0:20:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}将军阁下听说了你们的事迹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.10,0:21:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}特别给予你们参加国家炼金术师考试的资格
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.11,0:21:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}特别?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.47,0:21:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是你说让我们参加我们才…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.17,0:21:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}军队里的重要考试 小孩子怎么能参加呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.86,0:21:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不觉得我让你坐上这趟车是件好事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.08,0:21:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}去不去参加考试是你们的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.89,0:21:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}当然了 当然要参加
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.17,0:21:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我一定要参加
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.38,0:21:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看起来 我们是被他们玩弄于股掌之间呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.41,0:21:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.49,0:22:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们还没有力量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.31,0:22:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}找到了 在这儿在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.12,0:22:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小玛琳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.54,0:22:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大哥哥 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.57,0:22:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.88,0:23:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}钢之炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.57,0:23:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}第六集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.72,0:23:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}国家炼金术师资格考试
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.75,0:23:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}除了我以外没有人相信哥哥能合格
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.06,0:23:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是 那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.66,0:23:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}奇迹之花盛开了
